<title>Installation de <application>Python</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>Python</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>patch -Np1 -i ../Python-&Python-version;-gdbm-2.patch &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-shared &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

